Customers also get access to the CloudTestr portal with access to real time dashboard with Test metrics, downloadable test case documentation and test results documentation.<br>
</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929575452-638422e7-5d4b" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929575452-638422e7-5d4b" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Can my internal teams use the CloudTestr platform?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Your internal teams will have access to the secure CloudTestr portal to review test case results, view/download test case documentation, and Quality dashboard for test metrics.</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929634405-cce13eca-1c12" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929634405-cce13eca-1c12" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Who creates, maintains and executes test cases?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The CloudTestr team is responsible for creating, maintaining, and executing automated test cases. However, prior to developing and running test cases, the Customer/SI Partner would be requested to provide inputs on customer specific personalization’s, test data and approve the test cases to be part of the scope of the engagement.</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929670600-b8e95b7c-23b3" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929670600-b8e95b7c-23b3" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Can CloudTestr test integrations?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Yes, integration testing is an important requirement for customers across enterprises.<br>
CloudTestr supports automation of integrations. We will work with customers to gather information on their integrations and automate.<br>
</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929762701-545e5a93-d633" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929762701-545e5a93-d633" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">What time commitment is required from customer business/SME's?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Once we review the documentation provided and access the application to understand the customer specific implementation, we would request time from your SME for any clarifications we need based on our review. This could be 1-3 hours during the on-boarding period.</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929789001-2351cad7-d9e1" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929789001-2351cad7-d9e1" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">How do you ensure security of PII data?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="minti_list wpb_content_element color-grey arrow" style=""><strong>Clients have 2 options when it comes to data masking. </strong><p></p>
<ul>
<li>Customers can subscribe to and enable Oracle’s Data Masking solution in their test environment before each testing cycle.</li>
<li>For customers who do not subscribe to Oracle’s fee-based Data Masking Service, Suneratech offers a free Data Masking solution that customers can run to mask sensitive data during each testing cycle.</li>
</ul>
</div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929878515-003b2aaf-7ce3" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929878515-003b2aaf-7ce3" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">How long does it take to have the automation ready post sign-up?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">We can have automation up and running in 4-6 weeks.</h1></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1586929705766-7688013b-93fb" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1586929705766-7688013b-93fb" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">When does Suneratech get engaged during cloud implementation?</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><h1 class="headline font-inherit fontsize-s fontweight-inherit lh-15 align-left transform-inherit " style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Suneratech will work with Customer/SI Partner to understand the implementation schedule and propose the best time to get engaged to provide customer/SI partner ability to rollout quickly without impacting quality. The ideal time to engage is early stages of implementation to start creating automated tests and leveraging them for continuous testing through SIT and UAT phases. For some customers, we have engaged during SIT phase to create automated tests to be used during UAT phases and post implementation support.</h1></div></div></div></div></div></div>
		</div> 
	</div>

			allow_resize: true,
			allow_expand: false,
			counter_separator_label: '/',
			default_width: 1160,
			default_height: 653
		};
		
				/* Automatic Lightbox */
		$('a[href$=jpg], a[href$=JPG], a[href$=jpeg], a[href$=JPEG], a[href$=png], a[href$=gif], a[href$=bmp]:has(img)').prettyPhoto(lightboxArgs);
					
		/* General Lightbox */

		/* WooCommerce Lightbox */
		$("a[data-rel^='prettyPhoto']").prettyPhoto({
			hook: 'data-rel',
			social_tools: false,
			deeplinking: false,
			overlay_gallery: true,
			opacity: 0.83,
			allow_expand: false, /* Allow the user to expand a resized image. true/false */
			show_title: false
		});

		
	    
		/* Transparent Header */
	    function transparentHeader() {
			if ($(document).scrollTop() >= 60) {
				$('#header.header-v1').removeClass('header-transparent');
			}
			else {
				$('#header.header-v1.stuck').addClass('header-transparent');
			}
		}
			
		/* Sticky Header */
		if (/Android|BlackBerry|iPhone|iPad|iPod|webOS/i.test(navigator.userAgent) === false) {

			var $stickyHeaders = $('#header.header-v1, #header.header-v3 .navigation-wrap, #header.header-v4 .navigation-wrap');
			$stickyHeaders.waypoint('sticky');
			
			$(window).resize(function() {
				$stickyHeaders.waypoint('unsticky');
				if ($(window).width() < 944) {
					$stickyHeaders.waypoint('unsticky');
				}
				else {
					$stickyHeaders.waypoint('sticky');
				}
			});
			
			if ($("body").hasClass("header-is-transparent")) {
				$(document).scroll(function() { transparentHeader(); });
				transparentHeader();
		    }

		}			
	    
	    
	    	
	    /* Fill rest of page */
	    			    			$('body').css({'background-color' : '#172124' });
	    			    
	});
	</script>
